---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="QAIL — The AST Protocol for Data" description="Use one typed AST from API to database. No hand-written SQL string interpolation in app code on the AST path. Built-in RLS and N+1 detection for SaaS backends.">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <header class="hero">
        <div class="hero-bg"></div>
        <div class="container hero-content">
            <h1 class="hero-title">
                <span class="hero-icon">🪝</span>
                <span>QAIL</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">The AST Protocol</p>
            <p class="hero-tagline">
                One query language. <span class="highlight">Every layer.</span>
            </p>
            <p style="max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6;">
                QAIL lets you build queries as typed objects (AST), then sends protocol bytes to PostgreSQL.
                This removes app-side SQL string interpolation on the AST path and keeps RLS and validation centralized.
            </p>
            <p style="max-width: 560px; margin: -0.5rem auto 1.5rem; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.6;">
                Plain English: your app builds a typed query object, not a hand-built SQL string. PostgreSQL still does normal parse/plan/execute on the server.
            </p>

            <div class="hero-demo">
                <div class="demo-compare">
                    <!-- Source: QAIL AST -->
                    <div class="demo-target" style="order: 1;">
                        <div class="demo-new">
                            <span class="demo-label">QAIL AST</span>
                            <pre
                                class="qail-code"><code><span class="fn">Qail::get</span>(<span class="str">"users"</span>)
    .<span class="fn">select_all</span>()
    .<span class="fn">filter</span>(<span class="str">"active"</span>, <span class="kw">Eq</span>, <span class="bool">true</span>)</code></pre>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="demo-connectors" style="order: 2;">
                        <svg
                            viewBox="0 0 100 200"
                            style="width: 100%; height: 100%;"
                            preserveAspectRatio="none"
                        >
                            <!-- Source (0, 100) to Targets (100, y) -->
                            <!-- 1. Postgres (Top) -->
                            <path
                                d="M 0 100 C 50 100, 50 50, 100 50"
                                class="connector-line"></path>
                            <!-- 2. Qdrant (Bottom) -->
                            <path
                                d="M 0 100 C 50 100, 50 150, 100 150"
                                class="connector-line"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Target: PostgreSQL and Qdrant -->
                    <div class="demo-sources" style="order: 3;">
                        <div class="demo-source-card">
                            <span class="demo-label">POSTGRESQL</span>
                            <pre><code><span class="kw">SELECT</span> * <span class="kw">FROM</span> users <span class="kw">WHERE</span> active = <span class="bool">true</span></code></pre>
                        </div>
                        <div class="demo-source-card">
                            <span class="demo-label">QDRANT</span>
                            <pre><code>&#123; "must": [&#123; "key": "active", "match": true &#125;] &#125;</code></pre>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="hero-cta">
                <a href="/docs" class="btn btn-primary"> Get Started </a>
                <a href="/philosophy" class="btn btn-secondary">
                    The Manifesto
                </a>
            </div>

            <div
                style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; align-items: center; width: 100%; max-width: 400px; margin: 0 auto;"
            >
                <div class="hero-install">
                    <code>cargo install qail</code>
                    <button
                        class="copy-btn"
                        onclick="copyText('cargo install qail', this)"
                        >Copy</button
                    >
                </div>
                <div class="hero-install" style="border-color: #f7a41d;">
                    <code style="color: #f7a41d; font-size: 0.75rem;"
                        >zig fetch --save ...qail-zig/v0.2.0.tar.gz</code
                    >
                    <button
                        class="copy-btn"
                        onclick="copyText('zig fetch --save https://github.com/qail-io/qail-zig/archive/refs/tags/v0.2.0.tar.gz', this)"
                        >Copy</button
                    >
                </div>

                <!-- Language Slider -->
                <div class="lang-slider-container">
                    <div class="lang-slider">
                        <!-- Duplicate content for infinite scroll effect -->
                        <div class="lang-track">
                            <span
                                ><img
                                    src="/icons/rust.svg"
                                    alt=""
                                    style="width: 20px; height: 20px; vertical-align: middle;"
                                /> Rust</span
                            >
                            <span
                                ><img
                                    src="/icons/python.svg"
                                    alt=""
                                    style="width: 20px; height: 20px; vertical-align: middle;"
                                /> Python</span
                            >
                            <span
                                ><img
                                    src="/icons/go.svg"
                                    alt=""
                                    style="width: 20px; height: 20px; vertical-align: middle;"
                                /> Go</span
                            >
                            <span
                                ><img
                                    src="/icons/php.svg"
                                    alt=""
                                    style="width: 20px; height: 20px; vertical-align: middle;"
                                /> PHP</span
                            >
                            <span
                                ><img
                                    src="/icons/java.svg"
                                    alt=""
                                    style="width: 20px; height: 20px; vertical-align: middle;"
                                /> Java</span
                            >
                            <span
                                ><img
                                    src="/icons/nodejs.svg"
                                    alt=""
                                    style="width: 20px; height: 20px; vertical-align: middle;"
                                /> Node</span
                            >
                            <span
                                ><img
                                    src="/icons/c.svg"
                                    alt=""
                                    style="width: 20px; height: 20px; vertical-align: middle;"
                                /> C/C++</span
                            >
                            <!-- Duplicated -->
                            <span
                                ><img
                                    src="/icons/rust.svg"
                                    alt=""
                                    style="width: 20px; height: 20px; vertical-align: middle;"
                                /> Rust</span
                            >
                            <span
                                ><img
                                    src="/icons/python.svg"
                                    alt=""
                                    style="width: 20px; height: 20px; vertical-align: middle;"
                                /> Python</span
                            >
                            <span
                                ><img
                                    src="/icons/go.svg"
                                    alt=""
                                    style="width: 20px; height: 20px; vertical-align: middle;"
                                /> Go</span
                            >
                            <span
                                ><img
                                    src="/icons/php.svg"
                                    alt=""
                                    style="width: 20px; height: 20px; vertical-align: middle;"
                                /> PHP</span
                            >
                            <span
                                ><img
                                    src="/icons/java.svg"
                                    alt=""
                                    style="width: 20px; height: 20px; vertical-align: middle;"
                                /> Java</span
                            >
                            <span
                                ><img
                                    src="/icons/nodejs.svg"
                                    alt=""
                                    style="width: 20px; height: 20px; vertical-align: middle;"
                                /> Node</span
                            >
                            <span
                                ><img
                                    src="/icons/c.svg"
                                    alt=""
                                    style="width: 20px; height: 20px; vertical-align: middle;"
                                /> C/C++</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p
                    style="font-size: 0.8rem; opacity: 0.6; margin-top: -0.5rem;"
                >
                    Native Rust • Universal C-API • FFI Bindings
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Benchmark Results -->
    <section id="benchmarks" style="padding: 4rem 0; background: var(--surface-2);">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Real Benchmark: N+1 Battle Test</h2>
            <p
                style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; color: var(--text-muted); max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"
            >
                Same query. Same database. Same 50-row result set with 3 JOINs.<br/>
                100 iterations, release build, buffer cache warmed.<br/>
                Snapshot run: February 2026.
            </p>

            <!-- Benchmark bars -->
            <div style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.25rem;">
                <!-- QAIL -->
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;">
                    <div style="width: 140px; text-align: right; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; color: #22c55e;">QAIL AST</div>
                    <div style="flex: 1; position: relative;">
                        <div style="height: 40px; width: 3%; min-width: 28px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #22c55e, #4ade80); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: flex-end; padding-right: 0.5rem;">
                        </div>
                        <span style="position: absolute; left: 40px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: #22c55e;">449µs</span>
                    </div>
                    <div style="width: 80px; font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-muted);">1 query</div>
                </div>

                <!-- GraphQL + DataLoader -->
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;">
                    <div style="width: 140px; text-align: right; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; color: #e535ab;">GQL + DataLoader</div>
                    <div style="flex: 1; position: relative;">
                        <div style="height: 40px; width: 5.5%; min-width: 50px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #e535ab, #ff69b4); border-radius: 8px;">
                        </div>
                        <span style="position: absolute; left: 62px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: #e535ab;">1.52ms</span>
                    </div>
                    <div style="width: 80px; font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-muted);">~3 queries</div>
                </div>

                <!-- GraphQL Naive -->
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;">
                    <div style="width: 140px; text-align: right; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; color: #f59e0b;">GQL Naive</div>
                    <div style="flex: 1;">
                        <div style="height: 40px; width: 100%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f59e0b, #fbbf24); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: flex-end; padding-right: 0.75rem;">
                            <span style="font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: #000;">18.2ms · 40× slower</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="width: 80px; font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-muted);">~151 queries</div>
                </div>

                <!-- REST Naive -->
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;">
                    <div style="width: 140px; text-align: right; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; color: #ef4444;">REST Naive</div>
                    <div style="flex: 1;">
                        <div style="height: 40px; width: 93%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ef4444, #f87171); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: flex-end; padding-right: 0.75rem;">
                            <span style="font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fff;">22.5ms · 50× slower</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="width: 80px; font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-muted);">~151 queries</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted);">
                QAIL executes one planned query on this path. Naive resolver/endpoint patterns can explode to <strong style="color: #ef4444;">151 round-trips</strong> without join batching.
            </p>
            <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
                <a
                    href="/benchmarks"
                    style="color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem;"
                    >View all benchmarks →</a
                >
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The Stack -->
    <section id="stack" class="features">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">The QAIL Stack</h2>
            <p
                style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; color: var(--text-muted); max-width: 550px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"
            >
                Four layers. One AST flows through all of them.
            </p>

            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <!-- Core -->
                <div class="feature-card highlight-card" style="border-top: 3px solid #22c55e;">
                    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
                        <span style="font-size: 1.5rem;">🧬</span>
                        <div>
                            <h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.1rem;">qail-core</h3>
                            <span style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: #22c55e; font-weight: 600;">THE AST</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                        Parser, transpiler, type system. Queries are typed data structures,
                        not hand-built SQL strings in app code. Schema validation at compile time.
                    </p>
                    <pre style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); padding: 0.75rem; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 0.75rem; margin: 0; overflow-x: auto;"><code><span style="color: #22c55e;">get</span> users <span style="color: #22c55e;">fields</span> id, email
  <span style="color: #22c55e;">where</span> active = true
  <span style="color: #22c55e;">order by</span> created_at desc
  <span style="color: #22c55e;">limit</span> 10</code></pre>
                </div>

                <!-- Drivers -->
                <div class="feature-card" style="border-top: 3px solid #3b82f6;">
                    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
                        <span style="font-size: 1.5rem;">🔌</span>
                        <div>
                            <h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.1rem;">qail-pg / qdrant</h3>
                            <span style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: #3b82f6; font-weight: 600;">NATIVE DRIVERS</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                        Protocol-level PostgreSQL driver with typed values and built-in
                        RLS context per connection.
                    </p>
                    <pre style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); padding: 0.75rem; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 0.75rem; margin: 0; overflow-x: auto;"><code><span style="color: #3b82f6;">let</span> driver = PgDriver::connect_env().<span style="color: #3b82f6;">await</span>?;
driver.set_rls_context(
    RlsContext::operator(<span style="color: #fbbf24;">"op-456"</span>)
).<span style="color: #3b82f6;">await</span>?;
driver.fetch_all(&cmd).<span style="color: #3b82f6;">await</span>?</code></pre>
                </div>

                <!-- Gateway -->
                <div class="feature-card highlight-card" style="border-top: 3px solid #a855f7;">
                    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
                        <span style="font-size: 1.5rem;">🚀</span>
                        <div>
                            <h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.1rem;">qail-gateway</h3>
                            <span style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: #a855f7; font-weight: 600;">AUTO-REST + BINARY PROTOCOL</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                        Zero-code API from your schema. Auto-REST with FK expansion,
                        policy engine, WebSocket subscriptions, binary AST wire format.
                    </p>
                    <pre style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); padding: 0.75rem; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 0.75rem; margin: 0; overflow-x: auto;"><code><span style="color: #a855f7;">GET</span> /api/bookings
    ?status.eq=confirmed
    &sort=created_at:desc
    &expand=routes,payments
    &limit=20</code></pre>
                </div>

                <!-- Workflow -->
                <div class="feature-card" style="border-top: 3px solid #f59e0b;">
                    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
                        <span style="font-size: 1.5rem;">⚙️</span>
                        <div>
                            <h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.1rem;">qail-workflow</h3>
                            <span style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: #f59e0b; font-weight: 600;">STATE MACHINES</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                        Declarative multi-step orchestration. Database queries,
                        notifications, and events in typed state machines.
                    </p>
                    <pre style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); padding: 0.75rem; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 0.75rem; margin: 0; overflow-x: auto;"><code><span style="color: #f59e0b;">Workflow</span>::new(<span style="color: #fbbf24;">"booking"</span>)
    .step(<span style="color: #fbbf24;">"validate"</span>, validate_fn)
    .step(<span style="color: #fbbf24;">"charge"</span>, payment_fn)
    .step(<span style="color: #fbbf24;">"confirm"</span>, confirm_fn)
    .on_error(rollback_fn)</code></pre>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How It Works — Pipeline -->
    <section id="pipeline" style="padding: 4rem 0; background: var(--surface-2);">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Every Entry Point → One Pipeline</h2>
            <p
                style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; color: var(--text-muted); max-width: 550px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"
            >
                REST params, text queries, or binary AST all converge to the same AST.
                Policy injection and schema validation happen once. SQL text output is optional for tooling/debug views.
            </p>

            <div style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <!-- Entry Points -->
                <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    <div style="background: var(--surface-1); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1rem; text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);">
                        <div style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">REST</div>
                        <code style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: #ef4444;">GET /api/users?active=true</code>
                    </div>
                    <div style="background: var(--surface-1); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1rem; text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);">
                        <div style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Text</div>
                        <code style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: #3b82f6;">get users where active = true</code>
                    </div>
                    <div style="background: var(--surface-1); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1rem; text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);">
                        <div style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Binary</div>
                        <code style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: #a855f7;">postcard::to_allocvec(&cmd)</code>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Arrow -->
                <div style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 0.5rem 0; opacity: 0.4;">↓</div>

                <!-- AST -->
                <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(34,197,94,0.15), rgba(34,197,94,0.05)); border: 1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.3); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.25rem; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
                    <div style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: #22c55e; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">QAIL AST</div>
                    <code style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #4ade80;">Qail &#123; action: Get, table: "users", cages: [Filter(active = true)] &#125;</code>
                </div>

                <div style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 0.5rem 0; opacity: 0.4;">↓</div>

                <!-- Policy Engine -->
                <div style="background: var(--surface-1); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1rem; text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
                    <div style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: #f59e0b; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">POLICY ENGINE</div>
                    <code style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-muted);">+ injects <span style="color: #f59e0b;">AND operator_id = 'op-456'</span></code>
                </div>

                <div style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 0.5rem 0; opacity: 0.4;">↓</div>

                <!-- Protocol encoder -->
                <div style="background: var(--surface-1); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1rem; text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
                    <div style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: #3b82f6; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">PROTOCOL ENCODER</div>
                    <code style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-muted);">Encode AST → <span style="color: #3b82f6;">Parse / Bind / Execute + typed bind values</span></code>
                </div>

                <div style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 0.5rem 0; opacity: 0.4;">↓</div>

                <!-- Database -->
                <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #336791, #4a7faa); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">
                    <div style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">POSTGRESQL (with PG-native RLS)</div>
                    <div style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: white; font-weight: 600;">1 query. 1 connection. Done.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Supported Databases -->
    <section
        id="databases"
        style="padding: 4rem 0;"
    >
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Supported Databases</h2>
            <p
                style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--text-muted);"
            >
                One AST. Two powerhouses. Cache built-in.
            </p>

            <div
                style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; gap: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;"
            >
                <div
                    class="db-card"
                    style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #336791 0%, #4a7faa 100%); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 16px; text-align: center; min-width: 280px;"
                >
                    <img
                        src="/icons/postgresql.svg"
                        alt="PostgreSQL"
                        width="64"
                        style="margin-bottom: 1rem;"
                    />
                    <h3 style="color: white; margin: 0 0 0.5rem;">
                        PostgreSQL
                    </h3>
                    <p
                        style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem;"
                    >
                        Relational • Transactions • ACID
                    </p>
                    <div
                        style="margin-top: 1rem; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius: 20px; display: inline-block;"
                    >
                        <span style="color: #22c55e; font-weight: 600;"
                            >Production</span
                        >
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="db-card"
                    style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #24a1de 0%, #5cc4f0 100%); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 16px; text-align: center; min-width: 280px;"
                >
                    <img
                        src="/icons/qdrant.svg"
                        alt="Qdrant"
                        width="64"
                        style="margin-bottom: 1rem;"
                    />
                    <h3 style="color: white; margin: 0 0 0.5rem;">Qdrant</h3>
                    <p
                        style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem;"
                    >
                        Vector • AI/ML • Semantic Search
                    </p>
                    <div
                        style="margin-top: 1rem; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius: 20px; display: inline-block;"
                    >
                        <span style="color: #22c55e; font-weight: 600;"
                            >Production</span
                        >
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="db-card"
